# Firebase config.
# lib/firebase_options.dart and android/app/google-services.json are committed
# with FAKE placeholder values so the app builds & runs out of the box (backend
# stays disabled until you run `flutterfire configure` to drop in real config).
# The native iOS/macOS plists are NOT committed - generate them locally:
ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
macos/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist
